<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>PDF JPG 변환</title>
    <!-- pdfjs-dist library -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdf.js/2.10.377/pdf.min.js"></script>
    <!-- jszip library -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jszip/3.6.0/jszip.min.js"></script>

    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/slider.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/slick/slick.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/slick/slick-theme.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pdf-to-jpg.css" />
    <style>
      footer {
        position: relative;
        margin-top: 110px;
      }
      nav {
        top: 0;
      }
      #Accordion_wrap {
        position: fixed;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .container {
        margin-top: 80px;
      }

      
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./nav') %> <%- include('./accordion') %>
    <main>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="upload-file">
          <h1 style="margin-bottom: 40px;">PDF 파일을 JPG로 변환하세요.</h1>
          <input type="file" id="pdfInput"/>
          <button class="do-convert" onclick="convertAndDownload()">
            변환 후 다운로드
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="drop-file">
          <div class="here">
            <img id="addImg" class="add-img" src="/images/folder-add.svg" />
            <span style="width: 250px; text-align: center;">클릭 또는 파일 끌어다 놓기</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="open-help">
          <span>도움말(클릭)</span>
          <img class="help-icon" src="/images/help.svg">
        </div>
        <!-- <%- include('./slick') %> -->
      </div>
    </main>
    <div class="help-modal">
      <div class="modal-overlay"></div>
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-content-wrapper">
          <img class="close-modal" src="/images/deletebtn.svg">
          <h1 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">사용방법</h1>
          <p>1. 업로드 영역을 클릭하거나 드래그 앤 드롭으로 PDF 파일을 업로드합니다.</p>
          <p>2. <b>"변환 후 다운로드"</b>를 클릭해 PDF 파일의 각 페이지를 JPG로 변환해 다운로드합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('./footer') %>
    <script src="/js/pdf-to-jpg.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
